text:
Hello Nico! Yes, same weird building. Only perk, don’t have to wait for the infamous elevator as we’re on the 3rd floor! ;) 
Do you like living in Place des Arts? How does your girlfriend like Rodeo so far? i’ve been thinking, maybe we could have lunch sometimes with Aélis ? It’d be nice to meet and chat. Take care!

Yes! Lets see when we can have lunch. I tend to have lunch outside every day with no specific plans, so I'm easy. Place des arts is alright, we tend to be weirded out by everything but it's a cool place. Rodeo seems fine but we're already feeling strange about how picky companies here are regarding taking holiday time. Otherwise it's been quite fun :)
